reviewText: Not your typical Christian movie!  This movie talks about real life situations and has round characters that really struggle.  I find myself both cheering for them and hating them at the same time, and learning from them too.  Great writing!
Great job by a mostly community people.  Good story line for today's world.
Very intense, Restin did a very professional job. He should go far with the right breaks. I am sure  his family is very proud of him.
